# 🧠 What Service Workers Can and Cannot Do

| Feature                 | Supported |
| ----------------------- | --------- |
| Intercept requests      | ✅         |
| Access DOM              | ❌         |
| Access cookies          | ❌         |
| Run background tasks    | ✅         |
| Store cache             | ✅         |
| Send push notifications | ✅         |

